There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the french is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the mexican is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the american is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is the turkish##1
12. the person eating banana is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
