.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
There 7 different types of food: onion, corn, broccoli, peas, spinach, lemon, orange
7 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 5. the person eating peas is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating lemon##2
 7. the person eating corn is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person eating onion is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person eating onion is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating corn##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
| Beverage   | coffee       | water     | iced-tea | juice  | almond-milk | lemonade       | 7up           |
| Food        | orange | peas | onion  | corn   | broccoli      | spinach | lemon |
| Pet        | pony         | mouse     | hedgehog | lizard | frog        | cat            | rabbit        |

