 4. the entrepreneur is between the chef and the police-officer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the chef is the person driving the train##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the nurse is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
