 9. the coach is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the analyst is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the doctor##1
12. the owner of the pony is the analyst##1
13. the architect is in the middle##1
14. the analyst is between the person drinking coffee and the firefighter##2
15. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1

