 4. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
14. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person traveling to prague##2

