 2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the writer is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
